Author: androjennous
Text: If I had a nickel every time my mom said “just have a banana”.  It was my first “handful of almonds” type of experience and has never stopped.

Author: cautionhotpockets
Text: I love it when I haven't eaten for days and finally get something at like 2pm only to be told I'm eating so much. Like it's just a salad and an egg white but ok??
